  "prompt": "What is the best website to buy customized T-shirts in India?",
  "response": "There are several popular websites in India where you can buy customized T-shirts. Here are some of the best options:\n\n1. **Printland** - Offers a wide range of customizable apparel, including T-shirts, with various design options.\n\n2. **Vistaprint** - Known for printing services, Vistaprint allows you to create custom T-shirts with your designs.\n\n3. **Teej** - Specializes in custom T-shirts and allows users to either upload their designs or choose from pre-designed templates.\n\n4. **Zazzle** - While it's an international platform, Zazzle allows for shipping to India, featuring an extensive library of designs and customization options.\n\n5. **aTPrints** - This site focuses on custom printing and offers a variety of apparel, including T-shirts for personal or business use.\n\n6. **Tshirtwala** - Provides a platform for designing personalized T-shirts, catering to both individuals and businesses.\n\n7. **Funky T-shirt** - Offers an extensive range of T-shirts that you can customize with your designs, quotes, and images.\n\nWhen choosing a site, consider factors such as pricing, design flexibility, shipping options, and customer reviews to find the best fit for your needs.",
